text: Nabiyow cagalah dambii kee sahi gita edde-lem usun duudak gaddaloolah anuk gaaduk kok wadirroowaanamih idini koo essera maray salaadaay agabuuy lakmisa mar√¢ luk Raaqaanamat leedeeh ruffu iyyeeh Yalli aben dambitteh lubbitte kak alfe mara kinni, tokkel usun ellecabo sinnik toomem yaaxige mara hinnon jihaadak Raaqeenimih sabbatah
